I"Ú<p>At some point in 2016, perhaps inspired by <a href="https://everygame.tumblr.com/">Every Game I‚Äôve Finished</a>, I started keeping track of every game I, well, finished. (Also, to keep track of spending, I keep track of every game I buy or receive. I‚Äôve always got an idea what my backlog is - at least, back to 2016.) Most of my prior game opinions have gone by the wayside as I toted them from blog to blog, but the question is whether any of them were worth saving. The answer is not really.</p>

